    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?69.html">快捷导航</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?68_1.html">潍博资讯</a></div>
      <span>潍博资讯</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">《山东省青少年美术书法双年展》在我馆开展</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="line-height: 31.5px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">阳春三月，万物复苏，春天给我们带来了生机和希望，而少年儿童是祖国的未来和希望，儿童美术教育作为基础教育和美育的重要组成部分，对孩子的成长起到不可替代的作用。为进一步发挥社会公共文化服务职能，提升青少年教育</span></span></span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px;">工作</span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span>3<span style="font-family:宋体">月</span>3<span style="font-family:宋体">日上午，</span></span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family:宋体">我馆联合山东省美术家协会</span></span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px;">、</span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family:宋体">少儿书画协会共同主办</span></span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px;">了</span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family:宋体">《山东省青少年美术书法双年展》</span></span><span style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 40px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px;">。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170306/14887879108613081.jpg" title="779977684557923764.jpg" alt="779977684557923764.jpg" width="763" height="600" style="width: 763px; height: 600px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本次展览包含各类绘画作品两千余件，手工作品一千余件</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，以及众多的书法作品。绘画作品有</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">儿童画、黑白线描画、版画、水彩画、丙烯画等形式，展现了多彩、独特的校园生活；</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">手工</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">作品全部由废旧材料创作，凸显学校生态文明、低碳环保与艺术教育的有机结合；传统书法作品，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">则</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">是师生弘扬中华传统文化的缩影。</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">通过这些绘画、手工、书法作品，</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">全面的展示了孩子们近年来的学习成果，代表了潍坊市乃至山东省少儿艺术教育领域的最高水平</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170306/14887881457317106.jpg" title="206985080930977664.jpg" alt="206985080930977664.jpg" width="768" height="608" style="width: 768px; height: 608px;"/></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">建设中国画都离不开优秀文化艺术的发展，优秀文化艺术的发展离不开一代代少年儿童的传承与发扬。青少年不仅仅是传统文化艺术的学习者，更是中国传统文化艺术的传承者和发扬者。</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">此次展览</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">旨在传承</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">和弘扬</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">中国优秀传统文化，展示广大中小学生积极向上、追求美好生活的时代精神及书画艺术素养。</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">不仅有利于</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我市少儿美术进行艺术上的交流、学习和提高，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">而且能够使青少年</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">接受艺术文化的滋养，得到精神上的洗礼和升华，使得中国传统文化的精髓不断得到发展和延续。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170306/14887881894094266.jpg" style="width: 552px; height: 653px;" title="25554334309481606.jpg" width="552" height="653"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170306/14887881907591215.jpg" style="width: 775px; height: 634px;" title="617753976864985878.jpg" width="775" height="634"/></p><p style="text-indent:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px"></span></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">潍坊市博物馆作为全市重要的综合文化展示平台，随着首家在博物馆系统设立的《孔子学堂》，以及《小书斋大讲堂》的开讲，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">其</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">教育职能向社会不断延伸，始终</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">引导全市少儿美术教育事业健康发展，</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">积极</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为少儿美术展示搭建交流平台</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，承担起对社会宣传教育的重要使命</span></span></p><p style="margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=499"></script></div>
      
